EXEC sp_rename 'Temp1','GTTWorld5'
truncate table GTTWorld_BI

Insert Into
GTTWorld_BI(date,FlowType,Year,Month,Reporter,ReporterCode,Partner,PartnerCode,Code,FourDigit,SixDigit,Item,Commodity,
Class,Volume,Unit,Value,Currency,lb,normval,normlbs,MOMPerc,MOMActualLbs,MOMNormLbs,
YOYPerc,YOYActualLbs,YOYNormLbs,YTDPerc,YTDActualLbs,YTDNormLbs,Avg5Year,Avg5YearVol)

Select  GTTWorld5.Date, Insert Into
GTTWorld_BI(date,FlowType,Year,Month,Reporter,ReporterCode,Partner,PartnerCode,Code,FourDigit,SixDigit,Item,Commodity,
Class,Volume,Unit,Value,Currency,lb,normval,normlbs,MOMPerc,MOMActualLbs,MOMNormLbs,
YOYPerc,YOYActualLbs,YOYNormLbs,YTDPerc,YTDActualLbs,YTDNormLbs,Avg5Year,Avg5YearVol)

Select  GTTWorld5.Date, GTTWorld5.FlowType, GTTWorld5.Year, GTTWorld5.Month,
GTTWorld5.Declarant, GTTWorld5.DeclarantCde, GTTWorld5.Partner, GTTWorld5.PartnerCde, GTTWorld5.Code,ItemTable.FourDigit,ItemTable.SixDigit,
ItemTable.item,CommodityTable.Commodity,ClassTable.Class, GTTWorld5.Volume, GTTWorld5.Unit, GTTWorld5.Value,
GTTWorld5.Currency, GTTWorld5.LB, GTTWorld5.NormVal, GTTWorld5.Normlbs, GTTWorld5.MOMPerc,
GTTWorld5.MOMActualLbs, GTTWorld5.MOMNormLbs, GTTWorld5.YOYPerc, GTTWorld5.YOYActualLbs, GTTWorld5.YOYNormLbs,
GTTWorld5.YTDperc, GTTWorld5.YTDActualLbs, GTTWorld5.YTDNormLbs, GTTWorld5.Avg5Year,
GTTWorld5.Avg5YearVol 

From 

GTTWorld5 Inner Join ItemTable on GTTWorld5.Code = ItemTable.TradeCode 
Inner Join CommodityTable on ItemTable.Commodity = CommodityTable.CommodityID
Inner Join ClassTable on ItemTable.Class = ClassTable.ClassID
